==United States attorney==
The United States Attorney for the Northern District of California represents the United States in civil and criminal litigation in the court. the United States attorney is Ismail Ramsey.

* Calhoun Benham 1850-53 
* Samuel Williams Inge 1853-56 
* William Blanding 1856-57 
* Peter della Torre 1857-60 
* Calhoun Benham 1860-61 
* William H. Sharp 1861-64 
* Delos Lake 1864-69 
